data.description: Discover Your Dream Home!  Nestled on over 4 acres, this 3 bed, 2 bath haven is just 15 mins from Southside Walmart and Flowers Hospital. Embrace country living with a 24x24 barn, perfect for hobbies or storage. Multiple fruit trees dot the landscape, offering fresh delights. Enjoy warm summer days by the vinyl-fenced in-ground pool or relax in the chain-link fenced front yard. With creek access and convenient city proximity, this property offers the best of both worlds. Your serene escape awaits!
